            "title": "金像影帝老婆離奇當「街」開雀局打牌   國際級男神戙高腳應戰娛樂圈雀后",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"金像影帝老婆離奇當「街」開雀局打牌   國際級男神戙高腳應戰娛樂圈雀后\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/8358d7b15ccf2009b158ad6dce347985/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250322/_2025032215004366264.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">金像影帝老婆離奇當「街」開雀局打牌   國際級男神戙高腳應戰娛樂圈雀后</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一年一度的ComplexCon香港由昨日（21日）起一連三日在亞洲國際博覽館舉行，作為國際潮流文化盛事，ComplexCon每年都吸引不少潮界名人及明星到場。今年有份設攤位的陳冠希昨日亦在自創品牌CLOT的展位現身。另外，還有大批明星到場參觀，包括MIRROR成員、「香港Figure教父」Michael Lau、李璨森及影帝梁朝偉太太、影后級人馬劉嘉玲等。\n\n</p>\n<p>ComplexCon香港的官方社交平台，較早前分享了多段展場內的影片，當中見到陳冠希現身CLOT的展位，他帶著同為潮人的李璨森到處參觀，另外還有劉嘉玲到場。劉嘉玲頭戴cap帽，穿上貼身黑色皮褲及黑色上衣，以型格打扮亮相，更在場內與Michael Lau打卡合照。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152494/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉嘉玲昨日到ComplexCon香港展場參觀。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8bb9d037cca58d1d61c903a2ac5b984c/2025-03/carinalau1208_1742611219_3593605832682446580_723494209.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉嘉玲昨日到ComplexCon香港展場參觀。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152495/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉嘉玲與Michael Lau在場內合照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2cc5ff49735cd9599968c1ecf659f78b/2025-03/carinalau1208_1742611219_3593605832682323704_723494209.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉嘉玲與Michael Lau在場內合照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152496/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉嘉玲更在場內打牌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1e3edfa03a326981088b59c85eb45080/2025-03/carinalau1208_1742611219_3593605832690641583_723494209.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉嘉玲更在場內打牌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152497/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉嘉玲以全黑打扮現身。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/19a21ddfb7c1952ddacd29665051f719/2025-03/carinalau1208_1742611219_3593605832732679832_723494209.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉嘉玲以全黑打扮現身。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152498/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉嘉玲戴上cap帽亮相。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/234fdcc583d383af47924723144d8127/2025-03/carinalau1208_1742611219_3593605832782947525_723494209.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉嘉玲戴上cap帽亮相。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152499/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉嘉玲在展場內大殺四方城。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f3782d7d18c29be27203902961552f31/2025-03/carinalau1208_1742611220_3593605832674085236_723494209.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉嘉玲在展場內大殺四方城。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152500/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉嘉玲與多名到場潮人打卡合照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e71c00bd162a3e9ef6770220cc32701d/2025-03/carinalau1208_1742611220_3593605832682441260_723494209.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉嘉玲與多名到場潮人打卡合照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152501/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉嘉玲以全黑造型亮相。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d4aa6f1a746f65bca46201cd32a8c177/2025-03/carinalau1208_1742611220_3593605832799810836_723494209.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉嘉玲以全黑造型亮相。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152502/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉嘉玲以全黑造型亮相。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8cca22cbd13671f08fb4f238a8a4648b/2025-03/carinalau1208_1742611220_3593605832875196119_723494209.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉嘉玲以全黑造型亮相。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152503/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉嘉玲與老公梁朝偉及陳冠希都是本地潮人代表。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a37b954118c0d936a152f90023578a0a/2025-03/carinalau1208_1742525175_3592884036926128997_723494209.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉嘉玲與老公梁朝偉及陳冠希都是本地潮人代表。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152504/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉嘉玲與老公梁朝偉及陳冠希都是本地潮人代表。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/963412d0925fb345bab886cd6ba50060/2025-03/carinalau1208_1742525175_3592884036993165714_723494209.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉嘉玲與老公梁朝偉及陳冠希都是本地潮人代表。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152505/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"ComplexCon香港的官方社交平台，較早前分享了多段展場內的影片。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d4f4b1a5134df30180bfb1873e58c029/2025-03/VS--COMPLEXcomplexMUSICComplexCon2025mirrorwearellokmannkisangfrankie729altonwongzInstagram-0_17_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        ComplexCon香港的官方社交平台，較早前分享了多段展場內的影片。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152506/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"官方發布的影片還拍到劉嘉玲與Michael Lau合照情況。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/80f015cf47cc62094bf0d4fab0d17d78/2025-03/VS--COMPLEXcomplexMUSICComplexCon2025mirrorwearellokmannkisangfrankie729altonwongzInstagram-0_12_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        官方發布的影片還拍到劉嘉玲與Michael Lau合照情況。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152507/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"官方發布的影片還拍到劉嘉玲與Michael Lau合照情況。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/820105822fda381d538e4b3fd21ba3d8/2025-03/VS--COMPLEXcomplexMUSICComplexCon2025mirrorwearellokmannkisangfrankie729altonwongzInstagram-0_07_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        官方發布的影片還拍到劉嘉玲與Michael Lau合照情況。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152508/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"官方發布的影片拍到劉嘉玲進場。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/12f4586c75b4d26d26fb9e91ec2c5827/2025-03/VS--COMPLEXcomplexMUSICComplexCon2025mirrorwearellokmannkisangfrankie729altonwongzInstagram-0_01_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        官方發布的影片拍到劉嘉玲進場。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152509/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"陳冠希昨日亦有現身會場內，向好友李璨森介紹攤位內展品。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d222d1486c7e27219e3cdf2a83ed3757/2025-03/VS--COMPLEXcomplexMUSICComplexCon2025mirrorwearellokmannkisangfrankie729altonwongzInstagram-0_02_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳冠希昨日亦有現身會場內，向好友李璨森介紹攤位內展品。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152512/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"馮德倫都有到場。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a46e04d1422349a0e61664f1ac66cc25/2025-03/VS----0_10__0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馮德倫都有到場。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152513/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"陳冠希戙高腳應戰。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0c093be413533cd4172e33f841ba405e/2025-03/VS----0_02_2_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳冠希戙高腳應戰。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>其中一段由ComplexCon香港發布的影片可見，劉嘉玲與陳冠希突然在場內「大戰四方城」，畫面相當有趣。更有網民現場目擊這位影后級人馬，與國際級男神陳冠希即場開檯，並立刻拍下影片。劉嘉玲向來是圈中著名的麻雀高手，有看過的影片的網民留言笑問陳冠希：「難道你不知道嗎？」\n\n</p>\n<p>其實今年的ComplexCon香港旅發局以「打麻雀」為題，在「潮流市集」特設特色體驗區，高度還原中式宴會及屋邨街坊麻雀耍樂場景，帶領旅客感受香港地道文化色彩。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152264/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"有關的體驗區內亦特設麻雀枱，入場人士可即席嘗試「開枱」。旅發局圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f131eecdf226345f24e75b592bbe94ff/2025-03/08_8.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        有關的體驗區內亦特設麻雀枱，入場人士可即席嘗試「開枱」。旅發局圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152265/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場派發限量版鎖匙扣。旅發局圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/19dd1d9ea816fdee6e34c71d07463105/2025-03/06_1_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場派發限量版鎖匙扣。旅發局圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152266/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場亦有特製巨型麻雀用具，包括「起莊」、「打骰」會用到的工具。旅發局圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eda35f3b2c52419cb21967ee82b8ec7c/2025-03/04_2_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場亦有特製巨型麻雀用具，包括「起莊」、「打骰」會用到的工具。旅發局圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152267/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"模擬區模擬八、九十年代中式酒樓裝潢。旅發局圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7bd2e314f6733b4ab9078400ebf360cd/2025-03/03_2_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        模擬區模擬八、九十年代中式酒樓裝潢。旅發局圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152268/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"兩個麻雀耍樂場景，分別以中式宴會及屋邨街坊麻雀耍樂為場景。旅發局圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ec4004ad18d0cee449ef0f75e8e36383/2025-03/01_5_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        兩個麻雀耍樂場景，分別以中式宴會及屋邨街坊麻雀耍樂為場景。旅發局圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>兩個麻雀耍樂場景，分別以中式宴會及屋邨街坊麻雀耍樂為場景，模擬八、九十年代中式酒樓裝潢，還原舊式飲宴麻雀耍樂現場，還原公屋街坊齊集走廊「開枱」實況，感受鄰里情誼，活現港人日常生活與麻雀文化的連繫，讓參觀者沉浸感受香港地道色彩。\n\n</p>\n<p>有關的體驗區內亦特設麻雀枱，入場人士可即席嘗試「開枱」。現場工作人員融入場景化身「酒樓知客」、「屋邨街坊」等角色，為「雀友」介紹麻雀玩法及術語等，帶領訪客投入「打麻雀」地道社區文化；現場亦有特製巨型麻雀用具，包括「起莊」、「打骰」會用到的工具，一眾「雀友」可以打卡留念。 現場派發限量版鎖匙扣，設計靈感來自復古酒店房間鎖匙牌，並融合麻雀圖案，讓訪客感受懷舊魅力。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2059655/即時-娛樂-金像影帝老婆離奇當-街-開雀局打牌-國際級男神戙高腳應戰娛樂圈雀后",
