        {
            "title": "鄧炳強到維園花展賞花 買花送太太稱「加分之作」｜Kelly Online",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"鄧炳強親臨花展賞花。鄧炳強fb圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/870b995b855bf3ca10b68b70ac8f8dde/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250322/_2025032214441648506.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">鄧炳強親臨花展賞花。鄧炳強fb圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>【花展2025/鮮花/玫瑰/花卉/鄧炳強】花展2025於上周開幕，保安局局長鄧炳強今日（22日）在社交平台表示，趁著周末特定到維園花展賞花。\n\n</p>\n<p>鄧炳強表示，「香港盛匯超級三月」節目豐富，今早特別到維園花展賞花，形容每個展區各有特色、繁花似錦，每個展區都各具特色。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152367/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鄧炳強在離開前特意購買一盆迷你玫瑰送給太太。鄧炳強fb圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d1d6f5f84f9c0914ef100fb4a80dd6c0/2025-03/486424974_614811794649603_6075186550839944101_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄧炳強在離開前特意購買一盆迷你玫瑰送給太太。鄧炳強fb圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152368/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鄧炳強趁周末親臨花展。鄧炳強fb圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/834cb9027a20410f3e87bf0497e409c5/2025-03/486143216_614811804649602_4766543388172238856_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄧炳強趁周末親臨花展。鄧炳強fb圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152369/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鄧炳強形容花展現場「繁花似錦」。鄧炳強fb圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/34b4dd543a078f3bb448b867a0d07788/2025-03/485869418_614811774649605_7527191982858729535_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄧炳強形容花展現場「繁花似錦」。鄧炳強fb圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>鄧炳強又提到懲教署展區，展出的花卉由在囚人士與小學生共同栽種，支持更生服務。他續指，花展還匯聚來自世界各地的展區，以花卉砌成各地名勝景觀，並表示自己最喜愛北京展區的頤和園花景，形容其「成幅山水畫咁靚」。\n\n</p>\n<p>鄧炳強透露，自己在離開前特意購買一盆迷你玫瑰送給太太，笑言這是「加分之作」。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2059654/即時-港聞-鄧炳強到維園花展賞花-買花送太太稱-加分之作-Kelly-Online",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-22 15:01:15",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
