            "title": "西貢的士自炒墮山坡　的士司機受傷",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"的士剷落山坡。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/9b003a9966edec55644f11adf8ce7579/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250322/_2025032214242239900.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">的士剷落山坡。fb：車cam L（香港群組）</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今(22日)中午12時24分，一輛的士沿西貢西灣路行駛，馳至近萬宜水庫對開突自炒，飛落十米深山坡下，的士司機一度被困，其後自行爬出車廂，沿山坡攀爬返路面，他報稱頸及腰部受傷，由救護車送院治理。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4152435/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"的士剷落山坡。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e3df5d9a56ecab1b104c4a95367f4be2/2025-03/01_2_15.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        的士剷落山坡。fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
